{"word":"Spices","slug":"spices","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Spices</b> In the formula for the sacred oil<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=6'>Exo 25:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=35&verse=8'>Exo 35:8</a><br/> Stores of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=20&verse=13'>2Ki 20:13</a><br/> Used in the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=29'>1Ch 9:29</a><br/> Exported from Gilead<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=25'>Gen 37:25</a><br/> Sent as a present by Jacob to Joseph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=43&verse=11'>Gen 43:11</a><br/> Presented by the queen of Sheba to Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=2'>1Ki 10:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=10'>1Ki 10:10</a><br/> Sold in the markets of Tyre<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=22'>Eze 27:22</a><br/> Used in the embalming of Asa<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=16&verse=14'>2Ch 16:14</a><br/> Prepared for embalming the body of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=16&verse=1'>Mar 16:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=56'>Luk 23:56</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=24&verse=1'>Luk 24:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=40'>Joh 19:40</a>"}]}